ginal Cover:'''<br />October 1, 1994\n|{{ISBNT|9781569713167}}\n|-\n|'''Hardcover Limited Edition:'''<br />March 1, 1995\n|{{ISBNT|9781569710517}}\n|-\n|'''Standardized cover:'''<br />February 4, 2004\n|{{ISBNT|9781593070946}}\n|-\n!rowspan=2|2\n|rowspan=2|''[[Hellboy: Wake the Devil|Wake the Devil]]''\n|rowspan=2|\n*''Wake the Devil''<br />(5-issue miniseries)\n|'''Original Cover:'''<br />June 11, 1997\n|{{ISBNT|9781569712269}}\n|-\n|'''Standardized cover:'''<br />February 4, 2004\n|{{ISBNT|9781593070953}}\n|-\n!rowspan=2|3\n|rowspan=2|''[[Hellboy: The Chained Coffin and Others|The Chained Coffin and Others]]''\n|rowspan=2|\n*''The Corpse''<br />(serialized short)\n*''The Iron Shoes''<br />(short story)\n*''The Baba Yaga''<br />(short story)\n*''A Christmas Underground''<br /> (from the ''[[Hellboy Christmas Special]]'')\n*''The Chained Coffin''<br />(from ''[[Dark Horse Presents]]'' #100\u20132)\n*''The Wolves of Saint August''<br />(from ''[[Dark Horse Presents]]'' #88\u201391)\n*''Almost Colossus''<br />(2-issue miniseries)\n|'''Original Cover:'''<br />August 5, 1998\n|{{ISBNT|9781569713495}}\n|-\n|'''Standardized cover:'''<br />February 4, 2004\n|{{ISBNT|9781593070915}}\n|-\n!rowspan=2|4\n|rowspan=2|''[[Hellboy: The Right Hand of Doom|The Right Hand of Doom]]''\n|rowspan=2|\n*''Pancakes''<br />(short story)\n*''The Nature of the Beast''<br />(from ''[[Dark Horse Presents]]'' #151)\n*''King Vold''<br />(short story)\n*''Heads''<br />(short story)\n*''Goodbye, Mister Tod''<br />(short story)\n*''The V\u00e2rcolac''<br />(serialized short)\n*''The Right Hand of Doom''<br />(short story)\n*''Box Full of Evil''<br />(2-issue miniseries)\n|'''Original Cover:'''<br />April 26, 2000\n|{{ISBNT|9781569714898}}\n|-\n|'''Standardized cover:'''<br />February 4, 2004\n|{{ISBNT|9781593070939}}\n|-\n!rowspan=2|5\n|rowspan=2|''[[Hellboy: Conqueror Worm|Conqueror Worm]]''\n|rowspan=2|\n*''Conqueror Worm''<br />(4-issue miniseries)\n|'''Original Cover:'''<br />February 27, 2002\n