 Mexico''<br />(one shot)\n*''House of the Living Dead''<br />(original graphic novel)\n*''Hellboy versus the Aztec Mummy''<br />(short story)\n*''Hellboy Gets Married''<br />(short story)\n*''The Coffin Man''<br />(short story)\n*''The Coffin Man 2: The Rematch''<br />(short story)\n|April 13, 2016\n|{{ISBNT|9781616558970}}\n|}\n\n===Trade Paperbacks: ''Hellboy in Hell''===\nAll ''Hellboy in Hell'' comics are collected in [[trade paperback (comics)|trade paperbacks]].\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n!style=\"background:#7d2428; color:#fff;\"|Number\n!style=\"background:#7d2428; color:#fff;\"|Title\n!style=\"background:#7d2428; color:#fff;\"|Collects\n!style=\"background:#7d2428; color:#fff;\"|Published\n!style=\"background:#7d2428; color:#fff;\"|ISBN\n|- id=\"Hellboy_in_Hell_1\"\n!1\n|''The Descent''<ref>{{cite web|last=Means-Shannon|first=Hannah|title=SDCC last gasp: Mike Mignola celebrates Hellboy's 20th anniversary|url=http://www.nypost.com/p/blogs/gamereport/sdcc_last_gasp_mike_mignola_celebrates_JtLtlPUkPNVnlrgqb6OOKJ#axzz2a6SN9gLk|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130823062516/http://www.nypost.com/p/blogs/gamereport/sdcc_last_gasp_mike_mignola_celebrates_JtLtlPUkPNVnlrgqb6OOKJ#axzz2a6SN9gLk|url-status=dead|archive-date=23 August 2013|publisher=The New York Post|accessdate=26 July 2013}}</ref> \n|\n*''Hellboy in Hell'' #1\u20135\n|May 14, 2014\n|{{ISBNT|9781616554446}}\n|- id=\"Hellboy_in_Hell_2\"\n!2\n|''The Death Card''\n|\n*''Hellboy in Hell'' #6\u201310\n*''The Exorcist of Vorsk''<br />(short story)\n|October 5, 2016\n|{{ISBNT|9781506701134}}\n|}\n\n===Trade Paperbacks: ''Hellboy and the B.P.R.D.''===\nAll ''Hellboy and the B.P.R.D.'' comics are collected in [[trade paperback (comics)|trade paperbacks]].\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n!style=\"background:#7d2428; color:#fff;\"|Title\n!style=\"background:#7d2428; color:#fff;\"|Collects\n!style=\"background:#7d2428; color:#fff;\"|Published\n!style=\"b